00:00:03.640 --> 00:00:05.960
Good evening ladies and gentlemen.

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:11.960
Mataji is on the way and will be with you in short time.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:15.440
I thought it opportune

00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:19.360
few minutes to run through by a recapitulation

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:23.600
the various aspects of the mechanism that lies within us

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:29.160
for those people who have come for the first time - excuse me -

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:33.640
many who might not have heard the earlier lecture in which

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:38.960
various aspects of the chakras and the two sides of the subtle body,

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:41.840
the left and the right side and then the central channel

00:00:42.040 --> 00:00:44.640
were discussed and explained.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:49.640
And perhaps I can recapitulate a little on the

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:53.280
nature or quality of the chakra that

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:58.400
is expressed and the purpose

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:04.720
of Kundalini awakening and the process of Self-Realisation.

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:08.960
Many of you will be familiar with the

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:11.840
word "chakra" but for those who are not,

00:01:11.960 --> 00:01:16.480
it's simply an energy center within us at a very subtle level

00:01:16.760 --> 00:01:18.960
which expresses itself in the gross

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:23.800
as the plexuses of the autonomic nervous system.

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:28.000
It expresses itself in seven plexuses.

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.840
We have the Mooladhara chakra

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:34.560
which is part of that chakra

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:38.400
which we refer to as the Kundalini

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:44.040
and which lies in the gross body at the area

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:48.960
right at the tip of the sacrum bone, at the coccyx,

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:54.800
and so it relates to the pelvic plexus, the sacral plexus,

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:59.720
the coccygeal plexus and one other plexus that

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.120
is located in that area.

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:05.600
So the Mooladhara chakra

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:09.920
is that center which controls our sex,

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:16.000
it controls the whole organic structure

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:19.760
both muscular and [skeletonic] of that area

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:24.480
so controls such organs as the prostate gland

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:28.800
and in men and women of course the sex organs themselves

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:32.120
and so diseases that are related to this area

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:34.960
are very much a matter of

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:38.960
equipped investigating and fixing

00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:43.960
damage which may have occured at the Mooladhara chakra.

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:47.360
Also the psychosexual problems as well

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:51.160
could be very much affected and corrected

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:54.120
by Sahaja Yoga at this center.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:57.920
So Mooladhara chakra is the base,

00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:03.320
it is in fact the center which Mother has nominated

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:08.920
as Australia's part in the whole mechanism of this universe.

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:11.640
At a very subtle level

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:17.720
countries play a part in the whole nature of evolution

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:21.960
and in a very incomprehensible way.

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:25.560
But as you develop in Sahaja Yoga you begin to understand

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:28.080
Australia has a very vital role

00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:31.600
as the root. Mooladhara means

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:36.400
the root, the root that on which everything stands.

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:40.120
And so as you deepen in Sahaja Yoga you'll understand

00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:42.840
what vital role we have to play.

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:48.120
In fact India is that center which is in the sacrum bone

00:03:48.320 --> 00:03:51.440
which is really a part of Mooladhara chakra

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:56.400
and it's the triangular bone in which the Kundalini sits.

00:03:56.640 --> 00:04:00.800
It's the center of purity, it's the center of holiness

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:04.960
it's the center in which the Kundalini itself resides

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:08.800
dormant and sleeping as the residual energy

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:12.760
which at an appropiate time in our evolution

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:15.480
spiritually has to rise.

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:19.720
So closely connected is the Mooladhara

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:21.920
and the Kundalini

00:04:22.080 --> 00:04:25.280
and they are considered the first chakra.

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:31.400
The quality as I said, of the Kundalini is purity and holiness.

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:35.720
The quality of the Mooladhara chakra is innocence

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:39.440
and out of innocence comes wisdom

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:41.960
and with that wisdom comes obedience.

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:44.840
All of these are qualities of the Mooladhara chakra,

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:48.440
which we find beginning to manifest

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:54.600
as this Kundalini energy begins to rise and purifies these centers.

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:58.400
This is the center which gets so badly damaged by

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:03.160
all sorts of negative forces which due to our

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:07.200
licentious life due to all sorts of

00:05:07.400 --> 00:05:11.160
rather bizarre attitude towards sex,

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:15.080
all sorts of impure relationships,

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:19.200
all sorts of the unholy relationships

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:23.200
which can and do damage that center.

00:05:23.400 --> 00:05:27.720
It's a center which is our chastity, both in men and women,

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:31.120
and if our chastity is assaulted,

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:35.000
then this center becomes quite badly damaged.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:39.160
It can be fixed, of course. This is the whole point that

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.840
Self-Realization, that each of these centers

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:47.000
can be managed in such a way that any damage can be neutralized

00:05:47.200 --> 00:05:52.000
and in such a way that the spiritual ascent can be a growing,

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:54.960
tremendous force within each one of us.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:58.400
But the damage is there especially in the west.

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:02.840
Mother has often said that this center in Mooladhara

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:05.200
is the most damaged center in the west,

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:08.400
just as in India this center of Nabhi chakra

00:06:08.640 --> 00:06:12.760
is the most damaged in the east.

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:16.240
If I say to you that the Mooladhara

00:06:16.440 --> 00:06:22.280
damage represents a sin against the Mother,

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:27.120
the holiness, the purity, then you might begin to understand.

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.840
If I say that this center here,

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:32.280
where the damage has occurred in the east,

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:34.720
is in a way a sin against the Father

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:38.400
the all protective Father, the Father that looks after everything,

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:40.960
then when we see so much corruption

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:45.440
and so much graft and so much of this abuse in the east

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:50.920
we know that they must surely therefore doubt that

00:06:51.080 --> 00:06:56.120
how the Father will in fact provide all that is necessary.

00:06:56.320 --> 00:07:00.360
So we've gone about damaging our Mooladhara chakra in the west

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:03.720
and of course people in the east, through their corrupt activities,

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:06.880
through their acquisitive attitudes,

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:09.720
through their materialistic obsessions

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.880
have damaged so badly this center

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.600
which is referred to as Nabhi chakra.

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:17.840
Getting back to the Mooladhara chakra you noticed

00:07:17.960 --> 00:07:21.240
how is connected to the left hand channel which rises

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:25.760
as you probably read in some of the readings [today],

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:28.120
as the Ida nadi,

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:33.040
as the left hand side of the subtle body.

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:39.080
And it rises and it becomes what we call the superego.

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:42.960
The next chakra of Swadisthan

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:48.360
is yellow, the yellow one. Just wait till Mother comes.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:21.680
So this Swadisthana chakra, as Mother has explained,

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:24.080
it's the creativity within us,

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:28.080
it's the center which gives us our projections,

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:31.200
it's the center which makes us capable of thinking

00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:34.400
and rationalizing and working things out.

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:40.360
It's also the source of the pure knowledge of the Divine.

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:44.560
It's also the place where all pure knowledge,

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:49.960
all the pure conditionings take place and settle themselves

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:53.600
in such a way that we become

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:56.560
ready for our spiritual ascent.

00:08:56.760 --> 00:08:58.760
It's also the center which gets very badly damaged

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:02.000
by impure knowledge and by too much thinking,

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:06.120
and too much planning and too much analyzing and rationalizing.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:08.960
You notice how it's connected on the right hand side

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:12.680
by this yellow channel which

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:18.880
is called as Pingala nadi and terminates in this yellow balloon

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:23.440
in the opposite side which constitutes our ego.

00:09:23.680 --> 00:09:28.720
This ego is our rational brain, it's the part of our being which

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:31.720
thinks and mantains and analyzes.

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:36.840
It's also the side of our brain, if we like to put it that way,

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:41.760
which seeks power, ambition, wants to dominate

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:45.120
and in its worst form, aggress others.

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:50.720
So in a way this two channels have been there for our use

00:09:50.920 --> 00:09:54.600
in our spiritual ascent but in so many ways we often abused them

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:56.960
by misusing the left side

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:59.960
through too much emphasis on emotional life,

00:10:00.160 --> 00:10:03.440
too much emphasis on worship without the connection,

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:06.280
too much emphasis on our conditioning,

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:09.040
too much emphasis on using spirits,

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:12.760
all the things which we've talked about in the preceeding lectures.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:16.960
Whereas on the right side we've damaged

00:10:17.160 --> 00:10:20.160
those aspects of the chakras to the right

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:24.240
which relate to our projections, our overthinking,

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:28.160
our rational thoughts, our dominating attitudes

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:29.920
and all of those things which have

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:32.080
created so many imbalances in the chakra.

00:10:32.280 --> 00:10:37.200
Because the chakra is a pure, vital center of energy,

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:42.880
intact and in its own way pure and untraveled.

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:47.440
What we do to it by imbalances of either to the left or to the right

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:51.680
we cause a constriction of or even sometimes a detachment

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:54.640
of part of that center in such a way that

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:57.600
we can even end up with such diseases as cancer.

00:10:57.840 --> 00:11:00.800
Cancer is in fact a complete

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:06.680
brake down, a construction which is lead to a separation

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:10.200
of one aspect of the center, which in term causes

00:11:10.400 --> 00:11:13.040
a separation in the cellular structure of the body

00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:15.480
and of course run away cancer.

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:21.200
Is the uncollective, if you like,  expression of that damage.

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:25.080
Then we have the Nabhi chakra which is the centre, as I told you,

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:28.720
which is often quite badly damaged in the east

00:11:28.920 --> 00:11:30.720
as much as the Mooladhara chakra

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:32.720
is the one which we damage in the west

00:11:32.920 --> 00:11:36.360
so too the Nabhi chakra is the one which due to

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:40.720
too much emphasis on money, too much graft and corruption,

00:11:40.920 --> 00:11:45.480
too much doubting that God the Father who look after us

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:48.840
and provide for us in every way

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:51.960
and so therefore damaging this center.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:54.200
This is the problem of the Nabhi chakra.

00:11:54.400 --> 00:11:58.040
But the essence of the Nabhi chakra relates to our evolution

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.960
it relates to the principle of the family life,

00:12:01.160 --> 00:12:05.960
it relates to the means by which we evolve in other words.

00:12:06.160 --> 00:12:09.800
Family structure is an integral part to the evolution

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:14.680
and so if Mother appeared to emphasize family life last evening,

00:12:14.880 --> 00:12:17.720
if She appeared to emphasize motherhood,

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:21.000
if She appered to emphasis the quality of love within motherhood,

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:24.320
not child bearing but motherhood,

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:27.200
then understand what She is saying -

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:30.560
we have to evolve to higher beings.

00:12:30.760 --> 00:12:34.280
When we move from the human stage,

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:38.080
when we move from the animal stage into the human stage

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:41.080
we knew that we had to move higher and higher.

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:45.800
Now we've reached that epitome of evolution as a human being

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:49.400
and we have to now reach the higher levels going further

00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:51.320
of becoming a spiritual being.

00:12:51.560 --> 00:12:53.600
Now if She is here to do the job,

00:12:53.800 --> 00:12:59.600
if She is here to takes us through that next stage in our evolution

00:12:59.800 --> 00:13:02.800
just keep yourself in that frame of mind where

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:05.720
it's a spontaneous happening that has to take place.

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:10.240
It's the terminal point, if you like, in the principle of evolution

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:13.240
as epitomized by this center here.

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:15.120
And so if She speaks forcefully

00:13:15.320 --> 00:13:18.760
about the qualities of a loving mother,

00:13:18.960 --> 00:13:22.760
if She speaks strongly about the nature of family life

00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:26.040
and how it is broken down in the west

00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:31.120
and if She openly admits that some aspects of Indian way of life

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:33.200
are not quite right,

00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:37.240
but predominantly there are many areas which are

00:13:37.440 --> 00:13:41.200
tremedously important and could be well emulated in our country

00:13:41.400 --> 00:13:45.480
please understand She is not supporting

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:49.720
just in a nationalistic way the Indian way of life,

00:13:49.920 --> 00:13:52.680
She is supporting those eternal qualities of evolution

00:13:52.880 --> 00:13:57.800
which thank God had been retained in that country which is still,

00:13:57.960 --> 00:14:01.760
potentially and in reality, the greatest spiritual country

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:05.480
that's now in existence in this world.

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:08.720
So this center is the center of our evolution

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:12.640
and it epitomizes the quality of joy through family life,

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:17.200
of satisfaction. It relates to our material wellbeing.

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:19.880
So if we don't have a good Nabhi chakra

00:14:20.040 --> 00:14:22.240
quite often we'll have problems with money.

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:24.960
Or the other way around if we have problems with money

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:28.640
or are constantly obsessed about material things,

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:32.880
so too we will have a very damaged Nabhi chakra.

00:14:33.040 --> 00:14:35.760
And of course all the organs that relate to this centers

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.280
have to be taken into account.

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:39.120
If you are suffering diseases

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:41.480
of the organs of say the stomach, the liver,

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:45.160
the spleen, the pancreas, the kidneys all of these areas,

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:50.760
it is either relating to the Nabhi chakra or the Swadisthana chakra.

00:14:50.960 --> 00:14:55.720
And then the heart chakra in a word is the center of security,

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.880
the security within us.

00:14:58.040 --> 00:15:01.280
In the center it's that center of security

00:15:01.480 --> 00:15:05.880
of knowing with certitude that Almighty God,

00:15:06.040 --> 00:15:10.800
through the quality of the Mother of the universe, Jagadamba,

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:15.240
that She will provide that nothing can assail you,

00:15:15.440 --> 00:15:19.400
nothing can bring you down, that you become fearless,

00:15:19.640 --> 00:15:24.800
that no matter whether you are a king or whether you are a beggar,

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:29.160
that nothing, nothing can assail you,

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:33.880
nothing can break the confidence that you are a human being

00:15:34.040 --> 00:15:36.600
and that the Mother of the universe is looking after you.

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:40.160
That's the quality of the center heart, the sacred heart.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:42.800
Then we have the left heart which relates to

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:44.640
the quality of motherhood,

00:15:44.840 --> 00:15:50.280
that security again which a baby must feel in the womb,

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:53.200
which a child feels in the arms of the mother.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:57.360
It's the quality of security, of that caliber.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:01.760
And so if there's a dis-relationship between the mother

00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:04.360
and those other members of the family

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:09.680
or you and your attitude towards your mother is not harmonious,

00:16:09.880 --> 00:16:12.680
then this left heart center will be in trouble.

00:16:12.920 --> 00:16:17.400
And so too on the right hand side is the center of the father.

00:16:17.640 --> 00:16:22.080
the father is the protector, the father is the one who takes care

00:16:22.280 --> 00:16:27.840
in a very firm, forthright way, as epitomized by Shri Rama.

00:16:28.040 --> 00:16:31.400
The great incarnation of Vishnu who came on the earth to show

00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:36.600
just how important it is to have that quality of fatherhood.

00:16:36.800 --> 00:16:40.880
Responsibility to the society, responsibility to the family,

00:16:41.040 --> 00:16:44.200
responsibilty to his wife and to his children.

00:16:44.400 --> 00:16:47.800
And so this is the center in which the father becomes

00:16:47.960 --> 00:16:52.720
that secure example within us

00:16:52.920 --> 00:16:56.480
wherein we feel and those around us feel

00:16:56.720 --> 00:17:01.760
that absolutely nothing can assail us, because we epitomize

00:17:01.960 --> 00:17:05.280
that quality of fatherhood which gives that security.

00:17:05.480 --> 00:17:10.320
And so diseases related to the lungs, the heart

00:17:10.560 --> 00:17:14.640
and many other subtler, smaller organs in that area

00:17:14.840 --> 00:17:16.840
are related to this center.

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:20.400
Then we have Vishudhi chakra about which Mataji spoke last night.

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:22.640
This is the center of the throat.

00:17:22.840 --> 00:17:26.400
This is the center of Shri Krishna,

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:29.280
the next incarnation of Shri Vishnu.

00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:33.040
And His incarnation was that of

00:17:33.240 --> 00:17:35.960
showing us that we are part of the whole,

00:17:36.160 --> 00:17:39.920
showing us that there is an All-pervading God,

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:45.560
showing us that we have to realize the Akbar, the Great.

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:48.680
Allah hu Akbar. God is great.

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:52.600
And we have to know with certitude that this All-Pervading God

00:17:52.800 --> 00:17:58.080
is the one who gives us that spiritual ascent.

00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:01.840
We have to have self-esteem, neither loving ourselves too much

00:18:01.960 --> 00:18:04.080
nor loving ourselves too little.

00:18:04.320 --> 00:18:06.360
And so it's the center of self-esteem.

00:18:06.600 --> 00:18:08.960
On the one side if we are feeling guilty

00:18:09.120 --> 00:18:12.120
or if we are feeling the desire

00:18:12.320 --> 00:18:15.600
