01:05:10.480 --> 01:05:14.320
And that is what happens to you, you lose your ego.

01:05:14.560 --> 01:05:16.040
In Sahaja Yoga also we have seen,

01:05:16.240 --> 01:05:17.840
some people who come to Sahaja Yoga,

01:05:18.080 --> 01:05:20.960
get into ego trips, because it's a habit.

01:05:21.200 --> 01:05:23.800
It's a very bad habit in the West to get into ego trips.

01:05:24.040 --> 01:05:26.760
You see, just they jump into some imaginary balloons,

01:05:26.960 --> 01:05:29.640
I don't know what, and they start thinking: "I am this, I am that".

01:05:29.840 --> 01:05:33.280
I'm quite frightened to see this fellow was quite a normal person

01:05:33.480 --> 01:05:35.760
till yesterday. Now what has happened to him?

01:05:35.960 --> 01:05:37.840
So you see this ego is such a thing

01:05:38.040 --> 01:05:40.320
that if one egoistical person comes in

01:05:40.560 --> 01:05:42.240
the another can take up from that person.

01:05:42.440 --> 01:05:44.160
It's such a horrible stuff is.

01:05:44.360 --> 01:05:46.560
They are very contagious, very contagious.

01:05:46.800 --> 01:05:48.360
and that's how you will find that

01:05:48.560 --> 01:05:51.400
one egoistical now, if the husband shouts the wife will shout.

01:05:51.640 --> 01:05:53.240
And the wife shouts then the husband beats.

01:05:53.440 --> 01:05:55.560
If supposing, one person just stops,

01:05:55.760 --> 01:05:58.080
not shouting, it will calm down, definitely.

01:05:58.320 --> 01:06:00.800
But the contagious disease goes on increasing

01:06:01.000 --> 01:06:03.360
that the children become shouters. It goes on like that.

01:06:03.560 --> 01:06:06.920
So the ego is a thing that one does not feel it,

01:06:07.160 --> 01:06:10.720
does not understand it and it goes on destroying you, all the time.

01:06:10.960 --> 01:06:14.960
And the ego gives you a self-importance, but not self-esteem.

01:06:15.200 --> 01:06:16.920
It doesn't give you self-esteem.

01:06:17.120 --> 01:06:19.520
It just gives you self importance, unlimited.

01:06:19.760 --> 01:06:21.160
But what have you achieved?

01:06:21.400 --> 01:06:24.240
So, to be the Spirit you become a humble person.

01:06:24.440 --> 01:06:28.960
You need to become absolutely humble.

01:06:29.520 --> 01:06:31.800
One gentleman once told Me

01:06:32.040 --> 01:06:34.880
that, "I've heard you are doing such great things.

01:06:35.120 --> 01:06:36.760
And I've known you for 25 years.

01:06:36.960 --> 01:06:39.640
I did not know that you are Mataji Nirmala Devi.

01:06:39.880 --> 01:06:43.320
I only knew you as Mrs. Shrivastava wife of such and such".

01:06:43.600 --> 01:06:48.320
And he was the High Court,

01:06:48.600 --> 01:06:50.440
Hague High Court's, German he is.

01:06:50.680 --> 01:06:52.040
And so, I said "All right".

01:06:52.240 --> 01:06:54.840
He said, "No, you are coming tomorrow to my house.

01:06:55.080 --> 01:06:56.960
You have to give me Realization. I never knew."

01:06:57.160 --> 01:06:59.840
So I said, "How did you come to know?" He said, "We have a...

01:07:00.040 --> 01:07:02.880
He is from the royal family, another maharaja,

01:07:03.120 --> 01:07:04.960
who had your photograph in his pocket.

01:07:05.160 --> 01:07:07.280
And he took it out and put it to his head". So I said,

01:07:07.480 --> 01:07:09.040
"What's the matter?" He said, "You see,

01:07:09.240 --> 01:07:11.760
I have a very bad heart trouble and Mataji cured me.

01:07:11.960 --> 01:07:14.360
So he said, "Look at the photograph". And he said, "Oh, God.

01:07:14.560 --> 01:07:15.560
This is Mrs. Shrivastava.

01:07:15.800 --> 01:07:19.000
I knew her for 25 years. I never knew she could even speak.

01:07:19.360 --> 01:07:22.840
So She speaks and not only She speaks to all them

01:07:23.080 --> 01:07:25.040
He said, "We can't believe it this woman could speak.

01:07:25.240 --> 01:07:28.760
Because what I known her for this, is she's a very quiet person".

01:07:29.000 --> 01:07:32.040
So for all practical purposes I'm a very quiet person.

01:07:32.280 --> 01:07:36.760
And then he, you know, then came and he got his Realization.

01:07:37.000 --> 01:07:39.040
And he's such a humble man, you won't believe.

01:07:39.240 --> 01:07:41.720
He's such a humble man. He said "I've found it".

01:07:41.960 --> 01:07:44.280
He's a very learned personality.

01:07:44.520 --> 01:07:48.200
There is so many like that, we have an ambassador of Spain

01:07:48.400 --> 01:07:51.560
who was another humble man, you see. And he came to Me and he said

01:07:51.800 --> 01:07:54.080
"Mother give me Realization, I've come to know about it.

01:07:54.280 --> 01:07:56.440
Of course on that level I don't talk to people.

01:07:56.640 --> 01:07:57.960
He got his Realization

01:07:58.160 --> 01:08:01.040
and if I'm sitting, say, on a chair he would not sit.

01:08:01.240 --> 01:08:02.640
He will sit on the ground.

01:08:02.880 --> 01:08:04.800
The governor of Kashmir, I think.

01:08:04.960 --> 01:08:07.600
This is a very different style thing in India is.

01:08:07.840 --> 01:08:09.760
I must tell you, we people are very different.

01:08:09.960 --> 01:08:13.280
Even a garbage cleaner becomes such a big governor here

01:08:13.480 --> 01:08:16.160
that it's impossible to talk. It's a very funny thing.

01:08:16.360 --> 01:08:17.720
I'll tell you a story.

01:08:17.960 --> 01:08:19.920
Once a garbage cleaner came to our house, you see.

01:08:20.160 --> 01:08:23.200
And I said, "All right, this is an extra garbage, you throw it away"

01:08:23.400 --> 01:08:26.360
So he said, "All right, I'm willing to throw it away, the garbage,

01:08:26.600 --> 01:08:28.920
but how much are you going to pay me? I said, "All right,

01:08:29.120 --> 01:08:31.120
if you say, I'll give you some 10 pounds or something.

01:08:31.320 --> 01:08:34.400
He said, "You Indians, you don't know any laws, rules, regulations

01:08:34.600 --> 01:08:36.640
this, that and started shouting at Me.

01:08:36.840 --> 01:08:40.960
And this gentleman of the Hague High Court,

01:08:41.160 --> 01:08:44.720
the chairman of Hague High Court, the judge was standing there.

01:08:44.960 --> 01:08:47.600
He came out, he said, "Why are you talking so loudly to her?

01:08:47.840 --> 01:08:49.600
This is not the way to talk to a lady.

01:08:49.800 --> 01:08:51.120
He said, "What do you know about laws?"

01:08:51.320 --> 01:08:52.800
He's the one who's in charge there.

01:08:52.960 --> 01:08:54.800
"Oh, you Indians, I know how terrible you are,

01:08:54.960 --> 01:08:56.000
you have no idea of laws".

01:08:56.200 --> 01:08:58.760
You see, he was the one who was taking bribe from Me actually,

01:08:58.960 --> 01:09:01.760
and he was telling off this fellow like this. There is no humility,

01:09:01.960 --> 01:09:03.840
there's no respect.

01:09:04.080 --> 01:09:07.520
A garbage cleaner talking like to the head

01:09:07.720 --> 01:09:10.640
of the organization which is dealing with law,

01:09:10.840 --> 01:09:13.760
who has written so many books on human laws, can you imagine?

01:09:13.960 --> 01:09:17.200
There is no sense of proportion in people, that, what are we?

01:09:17.400 --> 01:09:20.880
Why should we be so boastful, arrogant and rude.

01:09:21.080 --> 01:09:24.520
It's not good, it's not human, it's like animals behavior.

01:09:24.720 --> 01:09:27.520
It's not a good thing. We have to be gentle,

01:09:27.760 --> 01:09:30.280
absolutely gentle, because we are human.

01:09:30.560 --> 01:09:34.120
God has given us so much. What blessings God has given us.

01:09:34.320 --> 01:09:36.800
I find Australians still very much better

01:09:37.040 --> 01:09:38.760
than any other western people, I must tell you,

01:09:38.960 --> 01:09:41.720
whatever people may say about you. That's my experience is.

01:09:41.960 --> 01:09:44.240
And I always tell everybody "You have to learn a lot from them,

01:09:44.440 --> 01:09:47.320
because they are innocent people, they are simple and innocent,

01:09:47.560 --> 01:09:50.160
and all the time they want to know what's wrong with them.

01:09:50.400 --> 01:09:52.640
They are simple people. They want to know about it.

01:09:52.880 --> 01:09:55.600
But I'm just telling you be careful about this mister ego.

01:09:55.800 --> 01:09:59.520
He's a horrible stuff, it always comes up for nothing at all,

01:09:59.720 --> 01:10:03.800
and is of no use. It's an empty vessel that makes too much noise.

01:10:04.040 --> 01:10:08.400
So now today, we are going to again have the session of Realization,

01:10:08.600 --> 01:10:11.360
and this is the seven chakras on the limbic area.

01:10:11.600 --> 01:10:15.320
When you get the Realization, all these chakras

01:10:15.560 --> 01:10:19.720
get completely enlightened within you, as you progress,

01:10:19.920 --> 01:10:23.360
and all your centers get absolutely enlightened,

01:10:23.600 --> 01:10:27.960
and you get all these different deities awakened within you.

01:10:28.240 --> 01:10:31.200
Then the power that, you see, you receive first, is

01:10:31.400 --> 01:10:35.560
that you receive complete bliss and joy.

01:10:35.800 --> 01:10:38.920
Of course in the west, people feel joy at the last I must say.

01:10:39.160 --> 01:10:43.600
But mentally they understand, they become very equipped mentally.

01:10:43.840 --> 01:10:46.680
Dr. Warren, who is sitting before you, he was the same.

01:10:46.920 --> 01:10:47.800
I've seen with all of them.

01:10:47.960 --> 01:10:50.040
First, they become mentally very equipped.

01:10:50.240 --> 01:10:51.720
They know so much because, you see,

01:10:51.920 --> 01:10:53.680
the whole knowledge comes into their head first,

01:10:53.880 --> 01:10:55.320
for their brains are more developed.

01:10:55.560 --> 01:10:57.560
While the people who have heart more developed

01:10:57.760 --> 01:10:59.200
they first feel the joy.

01:10:59.400 --> 01:11:02.640
You know the Fiji people who were here yesterday, day before,

01:11:02.840 --> 01:11:04.760
I said: "How are you feeling?". "We are feeling the joy".

01:11:04.960 --> 01:11:06.760
Ananda [ra], there's a joy coming out.

01:11:07.040 --> 01:11:10.600
Because their hearts are open. So that is what happens to people

01:11:10.840 --> 01:11:12.880
who are too much mentally involved.

01:11:13.120 --> 01:11:17.320
This is what happens to them. And those who are

01:11:17.560 --> 01:11:20.240
involved in the heart, they start feeling the joy, doesn't matter.

01:11:20.440 --> 01:11:23.640
But the growth takes place, a transformation takes place.

01:11:23.840 --> 01:11:27.040
Overnight people have given up their drugs,

01:11:27.240 --> 01:11:29.320
their diseases, so many things have happened.

01:11:29.560 --> 01:11:33.800
But you must know that truth can be little shattering,

01:11:34.040 --> 01:11:35.840
to your preconceived ideas.

01:11:36.040 --> 01:11:40.720
But God cannot remain with you as He wanted to be.

01:11:40.960 --> 01:11:45.080
He is what He is, He will be what He has to be.

01:11:45.280 --> 01:11:46.960
You cannot command God

01:11:47.200 --> 01:11:50.960
that "You stay like this. Now I'm going to organize you."

01:11:51.200 --> 01:11:56.000
He has organized everything for us, we cannot organize for Him.

01:11:56.200 --> 01:12:01.000
He works the way He works, every time, every minute.

01:12:01.200 --> 01:12:04.360
for Him is all perfect.

01:12:04.560 --> 01:12:06.120
And for you also it will be because

01:12:06.320 --> 01:12:08.600
you will be living in the present.

01:12:08.840 --> 01:12:13.800
When you start living in the present, every moment is dynamic.

01:12:14.040 --> 01:12:19.400
You really become a dynamic person, not a cabbage, not a mad man,

01:12:19.640 --> 01:12:24.000
but a dynamic, wonderful person, who's rid of all his problems.

01:12:24.400 --> 01:12:25.760
Dr. Warren himself had

01:12:26.000 --> 01:12:28.720
blood pressure, I don't know all sorts of problems he had.

01:12:28.960 --> 01:12:30.920
And it's all got corrected. But there are so many

01:12:31.120 --> 01:12:33.640
who are sitting here, at least there are 30, 40 people

01:12:33.880 --> 01:12:36.080
who will tell that, how they got cured of their problems.

01:12:36.320 --> 01:12:39.800
So you all should just think that here is somebody

01:12:39.960 --> 01:12:45.520
who is just here for your benefit.

01:12:45.840 --> 01:12:48.200
And there's nothing to worry.

01:12:48.400 --> 01:12:50.440
That's all he was trying to tell you

01:12:50.680 --> 01:12:52.000
and I have to tell you the same.

01:12:52.240 --> 01:12:54.480
But this Sahasrara has to open out.

01:12:54.720 --> 01:12:58.160
In a way, if you start doubting Me, Sahasrara doesn't open.

01:12:58.360 --> 01:13:01.280
Because I am there. I must tell you I'm in the Sahasrara.

01:13:01.480 --> 01:13:03.400
That's the way, I am there.

01:13:03.680 --> 01:13:06.000
You can find out later on when you find pressures on you head,

01:13:06.200 --> 01:13:08.600
you have to take My name, otherwise doesn't open out.

01:13:08.840 --> 01:13:11.240
What can I do about? I am there.

01:13:11.440 --> 01:13:13.800
So you have to just not accept me or surrender

01:13:13.960 --> 01:13:15.480
or what are you going to surrender?

01:13:15.720 --> 01:13:18.040
Except for ego what do you have to surrender?

01:13:18.240 --> 01:13:19.720
So there's nothing to be surrendered

01:13:19.920 --> 01:13:22.080
nothing to be given to Me, nothing.

01:13:22.320 --> 01:13:26.480
Just you have to take more, become deeper and deeper and deeper,

01:13:26.720 --> 01:13:29.160
and a personality who is enriched.

01:13:29.400 --> 01:13:31.200
But in Sahaja Yoga there are no courses,

01:13:31.400 --> 01:13:33.760
nothing of the kind. You have to work it out,

01:13:34.040 --> 01:13:36.520
come to the center, it's a collective happening,

01:13:36.800 --> 01:13:39.440
It's not a single person, sitting at home.

01:13:39.680 --> 01:13:41.600
You all have to come,

01:13:41.840 --> 01:13:44.360
make your progress, progress further and further.

01:13:44.560 --> 01:13:47.240
You'll be looked after very well, with love,

01:13:47.440 --> 01:13:49.600
and you will see how people are transformed,

01:13:49.800 --> 01:13:53.200
how gentle they are, how nice they are, how kind they are.

01:13:53.440 --> 01:13:55.680
Maybe one of them may turn out to be egoistical,

01:13:55.880 --> 01:13:58.280
so you just treat him as a mad man. Can be, you see,

01:13:58.480 --> 01:14:01.080
who is used to this thing they go back, for again circle,

01:14:01.280 --> 01:14:03.480
and again they come back. But doesn't matter.

01:14:03.720 --> 01:14:06.480
So I have to request you that you must come on a Sunday

01:14:06.680 --> 01:14:09.680
where I would like to meet you all and today let us see

01:14:09.920 --> 01:14:12.120
how many of you feel the cool breeze.

01:14:12.360 --> 01:14:16.000
Now I would request you to take out your shoes and sit in a way

01:14:16.240 --> 01:14:22.040
that you are touching the Mother earth with both the feet.

01:14:36.040 --> 01:14:38.520
Sahaja Yoga is only meant for true seekers,

01:14:38.760 --> 01:14:41.920
not for people who are false people

01:14:42.120 --> 01:14:45.640
or who want to satisfy themselves with falsehood.

01:14:45.880 --> 01:14:51.440
You have to ask for truth and if you ask for truth, you will get it.

01:14:59.560 --> 01:15:02.800
Now the first thing as I told you before,

01:15:03.000 --> 01:15:07.200
you have to understand that

01:15:07.400 --> 01:15:10.920
you should not feel guilty. That is very important.

01:15:11.120 --> 01:15:13.560
Now somebody started arguing with Me,

01:15:13.800 --> 01:15:16.200
that "God has told me to feel guilty". Now again I don't know

01:15:16.400 --> 01:15:19.240
which God has told you. You see, all these ideas you you give up.

01:15:19.440 --> 01:15:23.160
Please do not feel guilty at all, because

01:15:23.360 --> 01:15:28.080
I'm saying that God is forgiveness, God is love.

01:15:28.320 --> 01:15:30.360
He's anxious to give you Realisation.

01:15:30.600 --> 01:15:33.760
He's extremely anxious that you should get it. The time has come.

01:15:33.960 --> 01:15:36.520
This is the Last Judgement. You see the resurrection time.

01:15:36.760 --> 01:15:41.880
You have to get it, there's no other way out

01:15:42.120 --> 01:15:44.880
for Him also because He has to save His creation

01:15:45.080 --> 01:15:46.920
and His creation are human beings.

01:15:47.120 --> 01:15:49.920
So please for Heaven's sake do not feel guilty.

01:15:50.120 --> 01:15:53.240
This is a very important time. If you are feeling guilty,

01:15:53.440 --> 01:15:56.440
you just tell yourself that "Mother I'm not guilty".

01:15:56.680 --> 01:15:57.920
That is the first condition,

01:15:58.160 --> 01:16:02.520
that you should not feel guilty at all at this time.

01:16:02.960 --> 01:16:05.600
All right. Then the second condition is that

01:16:05.840 --> 01:16:08.240
you close your eyes and put your hands towards Me.

01:16:08.440 --> 01:16:11.640
So that you understand that there is no mesmerism.

01:16:11.880 --> 01:16:13.960
Or for what I should mesmerize you? There is no...

01:16:14.160 --> 01:16:16.040
But you see you have to close your eyes and please

01:16:16.240 --> 01:16:21.200
don't open your eyes, because when the Agnya chakra,

01:16:21.400 --> 01:16:26.160
when your eyes are opened Agnya chakra

01:16:26.360 --> 01:16:28.800
doesn't allow the Kundalini to pass through,

01:16:29.080 --> 01:16:31.720
So please do not open your eyes till I tell you.

01:16:31.960 --> 01:16:34.320
Because as I told you, there is no mesmerism, nothing.

01:16:34.520 --> 01:16:35.960
It works like sunshine.

01:16:36.200 --> 01:16:38.320
So just pur your hands towards Me like this,

01:16:38.520 --> 01:16:42.560
on your lap, very comfortably. Very comfortably be seated.

01:16:42.760 --> 01:16:45.160
Extremely comfortably you all should sit down.

01:16:45.360 --> 01:16:50.320
Put both the hands with your fingers little bit stretched.

01:16:52.720 --> 01:16:56.160
And close your eyes. You can remove your spectacles, will help you.

01:16:56.360 --> 01:16:59.160
Or any malas(garlands) or anything you are wearing in your neck,

01:16:59.360 --> 01:17:02.080
which is heavy. If there's something heavy, or may,

01:17:02.280 --> 01:17:07.040
please take it out. Also one has to be

01:17:07.240 --> 01:17:08.760
little bit loose in the waist.

01:17:08.960 --> 01:17:12.280
If a, it's very tight something on the waist, you see,

01:17:12.480 --> 01:17:13.920
may be not good.

01:17:14.120 --> 01:17:17.040
So something, or in the neck, necktie or something,

01:17:17.240 --> 01:17:18.680
should be also loosen.

01:17:18.880 --> 01:17:22.800
Please put your hands towards Me. Just this.

01:17:30.480 --> 01:17:34.000
Please take out your spectacles please,

01:17:34.200 --> 01:17:36.360
because it affects your eyesight also,

01:17:36.640 --> 01:17:39.280
It might improve your eyesight.

01:17:39.520 --> 01:17:41.240
Both the hands towards Me.

01:17:41.440 --> 01:17:47.200
Both the hands towards Me, like this, on your lap.

01:17:55.920 --> 01:18:00.480
Now, as I told you, the left hand is the desire.

01:18:00.800 --> 01:18:02.640
So keep the left hand as it is.

01:18:02.880 --> 01:18:04.760
But as I tell you, you have to move the right hand.

01:18:04.960 --> 01:18:06.640
But don't open your eyes, please.

01:18:06.880 --> 01:18:08.760
Please don't open your eyes.

01:18:09.040 --> 01:18:13.800
Just don't open your eyes, that is very important.

01:18:15.800 --> 01:18:20.720
You must sit still and don't do any movements.

01:18:20.960 --> 01:18:23.560
Just keep it still.

01:18:23.800 --> 01:18:26.440
You need not bend your head or push it back.

01:18:26.680 --> 01:18:27.960
Make it straight, that's all.

01:18:28.200 --> 01:18:29.960
But no pressure on your neck.

01:18:30.200 --> 01:18:34.800
Sit in a way that is comfortable to begin with.

01:18:38.240 --> 01:18:44.240
Now, we have to put our right hand on the heart.

01:18:44.680 --> 01:18:48.960
Just on the heart. And to say,

01:18:49.200 --> 01:18:54.240
"Mother, I am the Spirit", with all confidence.

01:18:54.440 --> 01:18:55.840
Say it thrice.

01:18:56.040 --> 01:19:00.080
Because you are, you are the Spirit, no doubt.

01:19:00.280 --> 01:19:02.040
And that Spirit has to manifest

01:19:02.240 --> 01:19:05.240
to show you what glorious thing you are.

01:19:05.440 --> 01:19:09.200
You are not your ego, you are not your mind,

01:19:09.400 --> 01:19:12.760
you're not your body, but you are the Spirit,

01:19:12.960 --> 01:19:15.400
the reflection of God Almighty within you.

01:19:15.640 --> 01:19:19.240
So say it on your heart.

01:19:24.040 --> 01:19:25.800
Steady down, steady, steady down.

01:19:26.040 --> 01:19:29.680
Put your left hand towards Me, left hand towards Me, yes.

01:19:29.880 --> 01:19:34.080
